name: Informant (V)
Lore: 'The Empire''s network of spies and petty informants allows Imperial operatives to discover and react to Rebel assaults before they occur.',
Text: 'Deploy Undercover on table from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Peek at top X cards of opponent''s Reserve Deck, where X = number of opponent''s characters present with your Undercover spy. OR If your Undercover spy on table, peek at top card of your Reserve Deck.',
